<TEXT>
   Tom Cruise has nothing but good things to say
about ``Color of Money'' co-star Paul Newman and his skillet.
   ``He's a tremendous person, wonderful actor, a humanitarian, and
he makes great salads, burgers and scrambled eggs too,'' Cruise said
in the March issue of McCall's magazine.
   Cruise, 26, said he and the 65-year-old Newman talk frequently by
phone when their schedules keep them apart. ``He'll call just to
